            <ul class="w3-section w3-justify">
                <li>Price - 100 USD a month (for 4 one-hour sessions and code reviews).</li>
                <br />
                <li>Prepayment for 3 months (term for learning of one block).</li>
                <br />
                <li>
                    <div>
                        <p>In case you should fail to come to hold a session at the time and on the date we will agree upon,
                            the session will be considered to be held and my obligations will be considered to be fulfilled.
                        </p>
                        <p>
                            <ul>Exceptions:
