                </form>

            </div>


            <div class="w3-container w3-justify w3-pale-yellow w3-leftbar w3-border-yellow
            w3-padding-large w3-margin-24">
                <p><i>Now you might think it will take too much time and too many efforts.
                        You might start thinking that waisting 2 or 3 or 5 years on learning
                        is too much. You might be right. But think that if you do not make this step now,
                        in some 2 or 3 or 5 years you will look back and say to yourself: "If
                        I had started to learn all that stuff all these years ago, now I would alrfeady know it all.
                        I would already be a computer programmer".
                        So, do not stand still.</i>
                </p>
